---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SubstackFeed from '../components/SubstackFeed.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Charles Wilke is a writer, designer, and generative AI consultant helping small and mid-sized businesses make practical, grounded use of emerging technology."
>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
      <img src="/about.jpg" alt="" class="page-hero-splash" />
    </div>
    <div class="container page-hero-inner">
      <div class="label">// about the operator</div>
      <h1>Charles Wilke</h1>
      <p class="page-hero-sub text-muted">Writer. Designer. Generative AI Consultant.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container about-grid">

      <div class="about-body">

        <div class="about-intro">
          <!-- Portrait shown inline on mobile, floated right -->
          <div class="portrait-wrap portrait-mobile" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="corner tl"></span>
            <span class="corner tr"></span>
            <span class="corner bl"></span>
            <span class="corner br"></span>
            <img src="/cwilke.jpg" alt="Charles Wilke" class="portrait-img" />
            <div class="portrait-scanlines" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="portrait-label">// charles</div>
          </div>

          <p>
            In my day-to-day, I'm the architect of <a href="https://pos.toasttab.com/news/toast-expands-toast-iq-smart-ai-assistant" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Toast IQ</a>'s soul. A senior product designer and proud parent of Toast's first steps into this brave new world.
          </p>

        </div>

        <p>
          Before that, I spent years making games at Insomniac and crafting content for product at GoDaddy.
          Roles that taught me how technology lands when real people have to use it every day.
        </p>

        <p>
          Through Fellow Vector, I partner with organizations to translate AI from an abstract trend into
          a usable capability. 
        </p>
        <p>
          That might mean shaping content strategies, designing AI-assisted workflows,
          building custom tools, or leading workshops that help teams understand how these systems can
          support their real goals.
        </p>

        <p class="about-lead">
          I help small and mid-sized businesses make practical, grounded use of this emerging
          technology. Not for efficiency's sake, but to reclaim time for the work that
          actually brings them joy.
        </p>
        <p class="about-lead">
          I do this with less hype and a clear sense of what actually
          matters for our best work to effortlessly flow from us.
        </p>
        <p>
          My approach is collaborative and human-centered.
        </p>
        <p>
          I believe these tools should shorten the distance between you and the things you care about most.
        </p>
        <p>
          Your craft, your people, your next meaningful thing.
        </p>

        <p>
          Let's skip the trite "what can AI do" conversation. The better question is: what's keeping
          you from your joy? What would you build, explore, or finally get to if the tedious stuff
          just... took less time? That's where we start.
        </p>

        <a href="/book" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Book a Call with Charles</a>

        <hr class="divider" />

        <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">
          If you want to see what happens when this brain isn't consulting, check out the games,
          albums, Substack series, and other strange artifacts at my personal site!
        </p>
        <a href="https://charleswilke.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-ghost">charleswilke.com</a>
      </div>

      <aside class="about-sidebar">

        <!-- Portrait -->
        <div class="portrait-wrap portrait-sidebar">
          <span class="corner tl"></span>
          <span class="corner tr"></span>
          <span class="corner bl"></span>
          <span class="corner br"></span>
          <img src="/cwilke.jpg" alt="Charles Wilke" class="portrait-img" />
          <div class="portrait-scanlines" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="portrait-label">// charles</div>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <div class="label">// works with</div>
          <ul class="sidebar-list">
            <li>Small & mid-sized businesses</li>
            <li>Founders & operators</li>
            <li>Executive teams</li>
            <li>Associations & communities</li>
            <li>Conference organizers</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <div class="label">// disciplines</div>
          <ul class="sidebar-list">
            <li>Generative AI consulting</li>
            <li>Content strategy</li>
            <li>AI-assisted workflow design</li>
            <li>Custom tool development</li>
            <li>Workshops & speaking</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <div class="label">// contact</div>
          <a href="/book" class="sidebar-link">Book a call →</a>
          <a href="mailto:cwilke@fellowvector.com" class="sidebar-link">Send an email →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <div class="label">// fellow vector is</div>
          <p class="sidebar-note">
            Just Charles. One consultant, fully present in every engagement.<br />No handoffs, no junior staff.<br />You work with me directly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <div class="label">// recently on exploring l.ai.bor</div>
          <SubstackFeed limit={3} />
          <a href="/writing" class="sidebar-link" style="margin-top: var(--sp-xs);">Explore more →</a>
        </div>
      </aside>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: var(--sp-2xl) 0 var(--sp-sm);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .page-hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .page-hero-splash {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center center;
    opacity: 0.35;
  }

  .page-hero-bg::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(to right,
        var(--bg) 20%,
        rgba(8, 9, 15, 0.65) 55%,
        rgba(8, 9, 15, 0.2) 100%
      ),
      linear-gradient(to top,
        var(--bg) 0%,
        transparent 35%
      );
  }

  .page-hero-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-sm);
  }

  .page-hero-inner h1 { margin-top: var(--sp-xs); margin-bottom: var(--sp-xs); }

  .page-hero-sub {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ── Portrait ── */
  .portrait-wrap {
    position: relative;
    border: 1px solid var(--phosphor-dim);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .portrait-img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .portrait-scanlines {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(
      ellipse at center,
      transparent 35%,
      rgba(8, 9, 15, 0.7) 75%,
      rgba(8, 9, 15, 0.92) 100%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .portrait-label {
    padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    color: var(--phosphor);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--phosphor-dim);
  }

  .corner {
    position: absolute;
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .corner.tl { top: 7px;    left: 7px;   border-top:    1px solid var(--phosphor); border-left:   1px solid var(--phosphor); }
  .corner.tr { top: 7px;    right: 7px;  border-top:    1px solid var(--phosphor); border-right:  1px solid var(--phosphor); }
  .corner.bl { bottom: 34px; left: 7px;  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--phosphor); border-left:   1px solid var(--phosphor); }
  .corner.br { bottom: 34px; right: 7px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--phosphor); border-right:  1px solid var(--phosphor); }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
    gap: var(--sp-2xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-md);
  }

  .about-lead {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--fg);
    max-width: 55ch;
  }

  .about-sidebar {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-lg);
    padding-top: 0.25rem;
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
  }

  .sidebar-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-sm);
  }

  .sidebar-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-xs);
  }

  .sidebar-list li {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    padding-left: var(--sp-sm);
    border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .sidebar-note {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .sidebar-link {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--phosphor);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .portrait-mobile {
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .section {
      padding-top: var(--sp-lg);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: var(--sp-md) 0 var(--sp-sm);
    }

    .section {
      padding-top: var(--sp-lg);
    }

    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--sp-xl);
    }

    .about-sidebar {
      position: static;
    }

    .portrait-sidebar {
      display: none;
    }

    .portrait-mobile {
      display: block;
      float: right;
      width: 40%;
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .about-intro::after {
      content: '';
      display: table;
      clear: both;
    }
  }
</style>
